index 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000..7c49d7d4577c732d366c1ae08b2d8a2606604c6d
--- /dev/null
+++ b/candidates_r2/kepler_marketplace_gmv/prompt.txt
@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@
+The folder at `/private/tmp/kepler_marketplace_gmv` contains Kepler Handmade Market's October 2026 marketplace orders, treasury reference rates, and README. Calculate paid-order gross merchandise value in USD for October, excluding cancelled orders. Report the amount rounded to two decimal places without a currency symbol.
